column1: # Represents resources to be embedded in the generated assembly.

column3: Optional string. Specifies the file this file depends on to compile correctly
Required string. The name of any file generator that is run on this item.
Required string. The name of the file that was created by any file generator that ran on this item.
Required string. The namespace in which any file generator that runs on this item should create code.
Optional string. The notational path is displayed if the file is physically located outside the influence of the project.
Optional boolean. Indicates whether to display the file in Solution Explorer in Visual Studio.
Optional string. Determines whether to copy the file to the output directory. Values are: 1. Never 2. Always 3. PreserveNewest
Required string. The logical name of the embedded resource.
